{"word":"οὐ 17","slug":"οὐ 17","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n75886\" key=\"ou)17\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">οὐ μὴν ἀλλά,</orth> <sense id=\"n75886.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">nevertheless, notwithstanding, yet, still</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀληθῆ μέν ἐστι τὰ πολλά, οὐ μὴν ἀλλ᾽ ἴσως οὐχ ἡδέ᾽ ἀκούειν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg004.perseus-grc1:38\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.38</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.4</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg002.perseus-grc1:22\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.22</biblScope> </bibl>; so <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">οὐ μὴν ἀλλά . . γε,</orth> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg023:449b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Grg.\">Grg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">449b</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg008.perseus-grc1:263b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plt.\">Plt.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">263b</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n75886.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">οὐ μὴν ἀλλὰ καί . . ,</orth> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">not only so, but what is more</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg037.perseus-grc1